snippet: Simona Halep wasn't sure she would be healthy enough to defend her title at the hardcourt Dubai Tennis Championships, which start Monday, so she didn't enter the event at first....
lead_paragraph: Simona Halep wasn't sure she would be healthy enough to defend her title at the hardcourt Dubai Tennis Championships, which start Monday, so she didn't enter the event at first.

headline.print_headline: No Serena or Kerber as Halep Eyes Title Defense in Dubai
headline.main: No Serena or Kerber as Halep Eyes Title Defense in Dubai
